quran[148]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"S yisem n Öebbi, Aênin Ipêunun"
  1,2,"Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  1,3,Aênin Ipêunun
  1,4,Agellid n wass iqeîîiyen
  1,5,"D Keçç ay naâbed, d Keçç ay nepper d Amâ²iwen"
  1,6,Awi ya$ d ubrid iweqmen
  1,7,"Abrid n wid i T$atev; ur n wid i K isserfayen, ne$ n im$eôôqen"
  2,1,Alm
  2,2,"Appan Tezmamt, ur degs ccekk, d nnhaya i wid ipêezziben"
  2,3,"wid iumnen s tbavnit, ipéallan, ipseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at"
  2,4,"wid iumnen s wayen i k d irsen, akked wayen id irsen, uqbel ik, u, $ef laxeôt, nitni, pputebbten"
  2,5,"Widak, di nnhaya n Mass nnsen, widak, d isaâdiyen"
  2,6,"Wid ijehlen, s tidep, iâuva fellasen ma tnubav ten, ne$ ur ten tnubav. Ur ppamnen"
  2,7,"Isle$ Öebbi ulawen nnsen, akked imeééu$en nnsen. Irs le$yaô $ef allen nnsen. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar"
  2,8,"Ger yimdanen, llan wid iqqaôen: \"numen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru”; nitni, ur llin d lmumnin"
  2,9,"La xedâen Öebbi akked wid iumnen. Ur xedâen siwa iman nnsen, ur faqen"
  2,10,"Aîan deg ulawen nnsen; Irna yasen Öebbi aîan. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan, ilmend n wayen skiddiben"
  2,11,"Ma nnan asen: \"ur ssefsadet di tmurt\"! A d inin: \"nekwni d wid, kan, ipleqqimen"
  2,12,"Day maççi d nitni, s tidep, ay d ifessaden, maca ur faqen"
  2,13,"Ma nnan asen: \"amnet, akken umnen medden\"! A d inin: \"day a namen, akken umnen ije$lufen\"? Day maççi d nitni, s tidep, ay d ije$lufen, maca ur éôin"
  2,14,"Ma mmugren d wid iumnen, ad inin: \"numen\". Mara yilin weêêedsen, ar ccwaîen nnsen, ad inin: \"nekwni yidwen! Nekwni la nettihi kan"
  2,15,Öebbi ad Ittihi fellasen. Isnerna yasen lbwe$v nnsen; ddebdeben
  2,16,"Widak, d wid iu$en ttelfan s nnhaya; ur d issasay ssuq nnsen, ur pwanhan"
  2,17,"Tevôa yidsen am win issa$en times. Mi tnewweô ayen i s d izzin, Öebbi Iddem tafat nnsen, Iooa ten di tillas, ur pwalin"
  2,18,"Âaégen, gugmen, dre$len; ihi, nitni ur d ppu$alen s abrid"
  2,19,"Ne$ am usigna igenni, degs tillas, tirmegt, lebôaq. Pparran ivudan nnsen deg imeééu$en nnsen, mgal ssiâqat; ad nnestaôen si tmeppant. Öebbi Izzi i ijehliyen"
  2,20,"Qôib i sen iêwi lebôaq, iéôi. Yal tikelt ideg i sen icâal, ad ddun syis. Mi sen ixsi, ad êebsen. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, ad asen Ikkes timesliwt akked yiéôi nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci"
  2,21,"A yimdanen! Âabdet Mass nnwen ikwen Ixelqen, kunwi, akked wid i kwen id izwaren, amar a pêezzbem"
  2,22,"i wen Irran tamurt d usu, igenni d lebni; id Isse$li d aman seg igenni, Issuffe$ ed yissen ppemôa, d ôôeéq i kunwi. Ihi, ur pparrat tanudda i Öebbi, u kunwi teéôam"
  2,23,"Ma tellam di ccekk, $ef wayen id Nessers ar umdan nne£, awit ed tasuôep i p icban. Neccdet ed inagan nnwen, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,24,"Ma ur tessawvem, u, war ccekk, ur tessawavem, êezzbet i tmes isseô$an imdanen, id$a$en, ippuheggan i ijehliyen"
  2,25,"Becceô wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ar i nitni, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Yal tikelt ara ppuôeéqen, si ppemôa nnsen, ad inin: \"d aya is neppuôeéq, uqbel\". Ippunefk asen i ten icban. Din, jjwao nnsen d ayen iûfan. Degsen ad wekkôen"
  2,26,"Ih, ur Ikukra ara Öebbi, a d Ifk amedya n tizip, ne$ ip i$elben. Wid iumnen éôan neppa d tidep, s$uô Mass nnsen. Wanag wid ijehlen qqaôen: \"acu Ib$a Öebbi s umedya agi\"? Yis, Itellif aîas; yis, Inehhu aîas. Ur Itellif yis, siwa iballa$en"
  2,27,"wid ipôuéun lemâahda n Öebbi, deffir lmitaq iS, issemfaôaqen ayen id Iumeô Öebbi ad imlil, issefsaden di tmurt. Widak d imexsuôen"
  2,28,"Amek ara tnekôem Öebbi? Tellam temmuten, Issader kwen id. Sinna, a kwen Ine$, sinna, a kwen id Issider, sinna, $uôeS a ppu$alem"
  2,29,"D Neppa i wen Ixelqen ayen akw illan di tmurt; sinna, Izzi ar igenni, Iwqem it d ûa igenwan. Neppa, Issen yal cci"
  2,30,"Mi Inna Mass ik, i lmalayek: \"Nek ad Rre$ aneûûaf di tmurt\". Nnant aS: \"day a Pperrev, degs, win ara isfesden degs, ara izzizlen idamen? Wanag, nekwenti nesbuccuâ K s ccekôan, u Neôôequ yaK\". Inna: \"Nek, èôi$ ayen ur teéôimt"
  2,31,"Isseêfev akw ismawen i Adem. Sinna, Issken iten i lmalayek, Inna: \"efkemt iyI d ismawen n wigi, ma kunemti d sut tidep"
  2,32,"Nnant: \"gedha s yisseK! Ur nessin, siwa i a$ Teslemdev. Keçç, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Bab n ûûwab"
  2,33,"Inna: \"a Adem, efk asent ismawen nnsen\". Mi sent imla ismawen nnsen, Inna: \"day ur a kwent Nni$ ara: Nek Ssne$ tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan, u èôi$ ayen d teqqaôem, akked wayen teppeffrem"
  2,34,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\"! Knant, siwa Iblis. Iugi, u isme$weô iman is. Illa seg ijehliyen"
  2,35,"Nenna: \"a Adem, ezde$ keçç akked tmeîîut ik, di Loennet, eççet segs, s tawant, ayen i wen ihwan. Ur ppaéet ar ttejôa yagi, mulac a ppilim d imednas"
  2,36,"Ikellex iten Cciîan fellas. Issuffe$ iten id seg wanda llan. Nenna: \"ûûubbet, d icenga bbwaygarawen. I kunwi, di tmurt, i$imi akked zzhu, siwa tallit"
  2,37,"Adem iîîef awalen n Mass is. Issuref as. Neppa, s tidep, Issuruf, Ipêunu"
  2,38,"Nenna: \"ûûubbet segs, akken ma tellam. War ccekk, a kwen id tas nnhaya s$uôI\". Wid iddan d nnhaya, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  2,39,"Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nne£, widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen"
  2,40,"A yAt Isôail! Mmektit ed l$it iW, is ikwen Öeéqe$. Eîîfet di lemâahda W, ad Ïîfe$ di lemâahda nnwen. D nek iwumi ara têezzbem"
  2,41,"Amnet s wayen id Sserse$, itebbten ayen illan $uôwen. Ur ppilit d imezwura ara t iagwin. Ur ppa$et, s issekniyen iW, ayen ôxisen. D nek iwumi ara têezzbem"
  2,42,"Ur slusut, i tidep, tikerkas. Ur teffret tidep, u kunwi teéôam"
  2,43,"èéallet, zekkit, îîinzet akked wid iîîinizen"
  2,44,"Day a ppamôem ise$ i medden, a ppeppum iman nnwen? U kunwi teqqaôem Tazmamt. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  2,45,"Ssutret lemâawna n ûûbeô akked téallit. Ih, dayen iwaâôen, siwa i imeéluven"
  2,46,"wid iêûan ar ad mlilen akked Mass nnsen, u $uôeS, nitni, war ccekk, ad u$alen"
  2,47,"A yAt Isôail! Mmektit ed l$it iW, is ikwen Öeéqe$. Nek, Smenyafe$ kwen i imavalen"
  2,48,"Ëezzbet i wass ideg ur ippuoazi yiwen deg umkan n wayev, s wacemma. Ur tepwaqbal ccafuâa segs, ur tepwaîîaf, segs, le$ôama, ur ten ppaâwanen"
  2,49,"Mi kwen Nsellek seg ugdud n Ferâun, sâaddayen fellawen aâaqeb adiran. Zellun arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Ayagi d taluft tabarart, s$uô Mass nnwen"
  2,50,"Mi, yiswen, Nessemfaôeq ill, Nsellek ikwen, Ne$meq agdud n Ferâun, kunwi la tepwalim"
  2,51,"Mi Nga lemâahda i Musa, kuéet wavan; sinna, deffir es, teddam d uâajmi. Kunwi d imednas"
  2,52,"Sinna, deffir waya, Nsemmeê awen, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  2,53,"Mi Nefka, i Musa, Tazmamt akked ufraz, amar a ppeppwanhum"
  2,54,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: \"a yagdud iw! Kunwi, s tidep, tdensem iman nnwen, mi teddam d uâajmi. Ssutret ssmaê i Uxellaq nnwen; mmin$et, ppif i kunwi ar Uxellaq nnwen. Issuref awen. Neppa, s tidep, Issuruf, Ipêunu"
  2,55,"Mi tennam: \"a Musa! Ur neppamen yisek, d awez$i, alamma nwala Öebbi, âinani\". Tewwet ikwen id ssiâqa, kunwi tepwalim"
  2,56,"Sinna, Nerra kwen id, deffir tmeppant nnwen, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  2,57,"S usigna, Nerra yawen tili. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeôôuoen: \"eççet si téidanin is ikwen N$at\". Ur a£ dnisen, maca densen iman nnsen"
  2,58,"Mi Nenna: \"kecmet tamdint agi, eççet degs, s tawant, ayen i wen ihwan; kecmet si tebburt, s lekni; init: nendem. Ad awen Nsemmeê tuccva nnwen, a Nernu i iâaôviyen"
  2,59,"Wid idensen bedlen awal, ur d win i sen nnan. Nessers ed, i wid idensen, tawa$it seg igenni, ilmend n tucmitin nnsen"
  2,60,"Mi issuter Musa aman i ugdud is, Nenna: \"ewwet aéôu, s uâkkwaz ik\". Feggvent ed, segs, mrawsnat tliwa. Yal wa iéôa anda ara issew. \"Eççet, esswet, si ôôeéq n Öebbi. Ur ssefsadet di tmurt am imjaêen"
  2,61,"Mi tennam: \"a Musa! Ur nesteqnaâ bippa s yiwen n lqut. Nuj a$ Mass ik, ad a$ d Issuffe$ ayen d teggar tmurt: tizzegzewt is, axyaô is, ticcert is, laâds is, lebûel is\". Inna: \"teb$am a pbedlem ayen ilhan s wayen ixuûen? Üûubbet ar Maûeô, a n tafem, war ccekk, ayen tessutrem\". I$li d fellasen ddell akked ééelt. Sebbeben d urrif n Öebbi. Ayagi, acku llan ugin issekniyen n Öebbi, neqqen lambiyya, war ssebba. Ayagi, imi âuûan, u zgaren tilas"
  2,62,"Ih, wid iumnen, udayen, imasiêiyen, iûabiyen, kra iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad sâun arraz ar Mass nnsen, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  2,63,"Mi Nga laâqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: \"eîîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, mmektit ed i illan degs, amar a pêezzbem"
  2,64,"Sinna, deffir waya, twexxôem. Lemmer maççi d lfevl n Öebbi fellawen, akked uêunu S, a ppilim seg imexsuôen"
  2,65,"Ni$ tessnem wid, segwen, iccven di Ssebt. Nenna yasen: \"ilit d iddawen imaâfan"
  2,66,"Nerra p d amedya i imuddiren akked wid i ten id ineûfen, u d aâggen i wid ipêezziben"
  2,67,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: \"Öebbi, s tidep, Iumeô awen d a ppezlum tafunast\". Nnan: \"day a tettihiv fella$\"? Inna: \"ad iyi Isseô Öebbi! Ur ppili$ seg at war tussna"
  2,68,"Nnan: \"nuj a$ ar Mass ik, ad a$ d Ibeggen anta p\". Inna: \"Neppa, s tidep, la Iqqaô: tafunast ur wessret, ur meééiyet, garasen. Xedmet i wen d ippumôen"
  2,69,"Nnan: \"nuj ar Mass ik, ad a$ d Ibeggen ini s\". Inna: \"Neppa, s tidep, la Iqqaô: d tafunast tawôa$t, ini imfeooeo, ad iaâoeb w ip iwalan"
  2,70,"Nnan: \"nuj ar Mass ik, ad a$ d Ibeggen anta p. £uône$, s tidep, tistan ppemcabint. Ih, ma Ib$a Öebbi, a nepwanhu"
  2,71,"Inna: \"Neppa, s tidep, la Iqqaô: d tafunast ur taâtib si tyerza n tmurt, ne$ si tissit n yigran, tûeêêa, ur tepwacôev\". Nnan as: \"tura, tebbwiv d tidep\". Zlan p. Qôib ur ewqimen"
  2,72,"Mi ten$am yiwen, wa irra p id $ef wa. Öebbi Issuffe$ ed ayen teppeffrem"
  2,73,"Nenna: \"ewwtet ep s kra ines\". Akka i Issidir Öebbi lmeggtin. Issenâat awen issekniyen iS, amar a pfehmem"
  2,74,"Sinna, deffir waya, qquôen wulawen nnwen; cuban aéôu, ne$ kteô, di ta$eôt. Ih, llan iéôa iseg d pfeggiven isaffen. Llan, s tidep, wid ipceqqiqen, teff$en d waman segsen. S tidep, llan wid i$ellin si tugwdi n Öebbi. Ur I$fil Öebbi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  2,75,"Day tôe$bem a kwen amnen? Ni$ arbaâ, segsen, ssemêasen i wawal n Öebbi, sinna, mi t fehmen, ad as bedlen udem, u nitni éôan"
  2,76,"Mi mmugren wid iumnen, ad inin: \"numen\". Mi qqimen garasen, qqaôen: \"day ad asen tinim ayen i wen Imla Öebbi, a kwen nna$en yis, ar Mass nnwen? Day ur tepmeyyizem ara"
  2,77,"Ne$ ur éôin ara, Öebbi Issen ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaôen"
  2,78,"Garasen, at war ta$uôi, ur nessin Tazmamt, siwa ayen nnwan. Nitni $ilen kan"
  2,79,"A tawa$it n wid ipparun Tazmamt s ifassen nnsen, sinna, qqaôen: \"ayagi s$uô Öebbi\", iwakken ad a$en, yis, ayen ôxisen! A tawa$it nnsen, ilmend n wayen uran ifassen nnsen! A tawa$it nnsen, $ef wayen keppben"
  2,80,"Nnan: \"ur a$ tepnal tmes, d awez$i, siwa kra n wussan\". Ini: \"day teîîfem lemâahda s$uô Öebbi? Öebbi, d awez$i, ur Izeggil lemâahda S. Ne$ teqqaôem, $ef Öebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  2,81,"Xaîi, win ikesben tucmip, u tennev as tuccva s…, widak, d at tmes, degs ad wekkôen"
  2,82,"Wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, widak, d at Loennet, degs ad wekkôen"
  2,83,"Mi Nga laâqed i At Isôail: \"ur âabdet siwa Öebbi. Elhut ar imawlan, ar llzem nnwen, ar igujilen, ar igellilen. Init i medden, awal imaânen. èéÈallet, zekkit\". Sinna, twexxôem, siwa kra segwen, u, kunwi, tnumrem"
  2,84,"Mi wen Nga laâqed nnwen: \"ur zzazalet idim nnwen, ur pemssuffu$et seg ixxamen nnwen\". D$a twefqem, kunwi d inagan"
  2,85,"Sinna, kunwi d wid immin$en, tessuff$em arbaâ segwen, seg ixxamen nnsen. Tezzim asen s ibekkaven akked taâdawt. Ma usan kwen id, d imeêbas, tfeddum ten. Irna, ipwagdel awen usuffe$ nnsen. Day tumnem deg uêric n Tezmamt, tnekôem wayev? Anwa ay d arraz n wid, segwen, ixedmen aya, ma maççi d ddell, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u, ass n tnekra, ad ppunefken i uâaqeb uqsiê mavi? Ur I$fil Öebbi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  2,86,"Widak d wid iu$en tudert n ddunit s laxeôt, ur ippifsus fellasen uâaqeb, ur ppusellken"
  2,87,"Ni$ Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Nuzen ed imazanen, deffir es. Nefka abeggen i Âisa, mmi s n Meryem, Null it s ôôuê iqedsen. Yal tikelt ideg ara kwen id ias umazan, s wayen ur awen nehwi, tesme$wôem iman nnwen. Kra teskaddbem ten, kra ten$am ten"
  2,88,"Nnan: \"ulawen nne$ qquôen\". Xaîi, Ixza ten Öebbi, ilmend n tijehli nnsen. Drus iten wid iumnen"
  2,89,"Mi ten id tusa Tezmamt, s$uô Öebbi, d atebbet n wayen illan $uôsen, - u llan, iu$ lêal, ssuturen ad $elben wid ijehlen - mi ten id iusa wayen ssnen, ugin t. Ad Inâal Öebbi ijehliyen"
  2,90,"I icmet wayen i$ef zzenzen iman nnsen! Ugin ayen id Issers Öebbi. Ëesden mi id Issers Öebbi, si lfevl iS, i win i S ihwan n yimdanen iS. Sebbeben urrif ar wayev. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb isdullun"
  2,91,"Ma nnan asen: \"amnet s wayen id Issers Öebbi\"! A d inin: \"numen s wayen id irsen $uône$\". Nekôen ayen i t id itebâan, u neppa d tidep, d atebbet n wayen illan $uôsen. Ini: \"acimi tneqqem lambiyya n Öebbi, zik, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  2,92,"Ni$ iusa kwen id Musa, s ubeggen. Sinna, deffir es, teddam akked uâajmi. Kunwi d imednas"
  2,93,"Mi Nga laâqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: \"eîîfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, u ssemêesset\". Nnan d: \"nesla u nâuûa\". Ikecm asen uâajmi ar wul, si tjehli nnsen. Ini: \"dir it wayen i wen iumeô liman nnwen, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  2,94,"Ini: \"maday, ar Öebbi, axxam aneggaru i kunwi kan, ur pkkan ara imdanen, mennit tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,95,"D awez$i, ur p pmennin, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnsen. Öebbi Issen imednas"
  2,96,"A ten tafev, war ccekk, êemmlen tameddurt sennig medden, sennig imcurak. Atan yiwen segsen, issaram ad idder agim iseggwasen. Te$wzi n laâmeô is, ur as tessifrir aâaqeb. Öebbi Ipwali ayen xeddmen"
  2,97,"Ini: \"anwa illan d acengu n Jebrayen\"? D neppa, s tidep, it id issersen $ef wul ik, s leb$i n Öebbi. D atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d nnhaya u d abecceô n lmumnin"
  2,98,"Win illan d acengu n Öebbi, lmalayek iS, imazanen iS, Jebrayen, Mikail…, ihi, Öebbi d acengu ijehliyen"
  2,99,"Ni$ Nessers ak d issekniyen iberrzen. I ten inekôen, siwa iballa$en"
  2,100,"Day yal tikelt ideg ara gen laâqed, a t ixdaâ urbaâ segsen? Ih, tegwti segsen, ur uminen"
  2,101,"Mi ten id iusa umazan s$uô Öebbi, itebbet ayen illan $uôsen, arbaâ n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, rran Tazmamt n Öebbi s azagur nnsen, amzun ur ssinen"
  2,102,"Ddan akked wayen xedmen ccwaîen mgal tagelda n Sliman. Sliman ur ijhil. Maca ccwaîen jehlen. Sseêfaven i medden ssêur, akked wayen id irsen, di Babil, ar lmalayek Harut akked Marut. Ur sselmaden yiwen, mebla ma nnan: \"nekwni n$ewwu kan, ur jehhel\"! ÊÊÊËefven, $uôsen, amek ara ssemfaôaqen argaz akked tmeîîut is. Ur îîurun yiwen syis, siwa ma Ib$a Öebbi. ÊÊÊËefven ara ten ivuôôen, ur ten ineffaâ. Ni$ éôan ar win i p iu$en, ur as illi umur di laxeôt. War ccekk, ard ucmit wayen is zzenzen leôwaê nnsen, lemmer éôin"
  2,103,"Lemmer, s tidep, uminen u êezzben, ad ifrir warraz s$uô Öebbi, lemmer ssinen"
  2,104,"A wid iumnen! Ur qqaret: \"Âass a$ d\", init: \"Wali a$ d\", u ssemêesset. I ijehliyen, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  2,105,"Ur b$in ara ijehliyen, seg wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, akked imcurak, ad awen d irs kra n lxiô, s$uô Mass nnwen. Öebbi Ismenyaf, s uêunu S, win i S ihwan. Öebbi d Bab n lfevl ameqwôaêan"
  2,106,"Ur Nessemsay assekni, ne$ ur t Nesseppu, mebla ma Nebbwi d win it yifen, ne$ i t icban. Day ur teéôiv ara Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  2,107,"Day ur teéôiv ara, ar n Öebbi tagelda n tmurt akked igenwan? Ur tesâim, war Öebbi, bab, ne$ asettaô"
  2,108,"Ne$ teb$am a ppesteqsim Amazan nnwen, akken ippusteqsa, zik, Musa? Win ibeddlen liman s tijehli, innetlaf ar yir abrid"
  2,109,"Si leêsed nnsen, aîas seg wAt Tezmamt, mi sen d tban tidep, budden awen tijehli, mbaâd liman nnwen. Ssemêet, ssemsut, ar d Ias Öebbi s lameô iS. Ni$ Öebbi Izmer i yal cci"
  2,110,"èéallet, zekkit. Ayen ara tezzewrem n lxiô i iman nnwen, a t tafem ar Öebbi. Öebbi, s tidep, Ipwali ayen akw txeddmem"
  2,111,"Nnan: \"ur ikeççem Loennet, siwa win illan d uday, ne$ d amasiêi\". D wagi ay d asirem nnsen. Ini: \"awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,112,"Xaîi, win iunzen i Öebbi, u d aâôvi, ad isâu arraz is, ar Mass is. Ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  2,113,"Nnan wudayen: \"imasiêiyen ur sennden s acemma\". Nnan imasiêiyen: \"udayen ur sennden s acemma\". U nitni la qqaôen Tazmamt. Akka, wid ur nessin ara, nnan am nitni. Ad Iêudd Öebbi, garasen, ass n tnekra, $ef wayen i$ef mgarraden"
  2,114,"Anwa idensen sennig wid igedlen, di leowamaâ n Öebbi, asmekti n yisem iS, u lhan d deg ussexôeb nnsen? Widak, ur iwata ara a ten kecmen, siwa ma s tugwdi. I nitni, ddell di ddunit, u aâaqeb abarar di laxeôt"
  2,115,"N Öebbi agmuv akked utaram. Ar wanda tezzim, din Udem n Öebbi. Ih, Öebbi d Ajemmal, d Amusnaw"
  2,116,"Nnan: \"Öebbi Isâa mmi S\". Gedha s yiS! Ni$ ineS i illan di tmurt akked igenwan. Akw, péallan i Neppa"
  2,117,"Axellaq n tmurt akked igenwan. Ma Iseyya lameô, ad as Yini kan: \"ili\"! Ad yili"
  2,118,"Nnan wid ur nessin: \"a lemmer ad a$ d Immeslay Öebbi, ne$ ad a$ d ias ussekni\"! Akka ay nnan wid i ten id izwaren, am awalen nnsen. Ppemcabin wulawen nnsen. Ni$ Nbeggen ed issekniyen i ugdud ipputebbten"
  2,119,"Ih, Nuzen ik id, s tidep, d abcir, u d aneddaô. Ur ippili fellak usteqsi $ef at wu$ud"
  2,120,"Ur k pôavin wudayen ne$ imasiêiyen, alamma teddiv d ddin nnsen. Ini: \"d nehhu n Öebbi ay d nehhu\". Ma teddiv akked usirem nnsen, deffir wayen ik ed iusan n tmusni, ur k ipfukku, si Öebbi, bab, ne$ asettaô"
  2,121,"Wid iwumi Nefka Tazmamt, qqaôen p leqôaya iwatan. Widak umnen yis. Wid i p iugin, widak d imexsuôen"
  2,122,"A yAt Isôail! Mmektit ed l$it iW, is i kwen £ate$. Nek, Smenyafe$ kwen i imavalen"
  2,123,"Ëezzbet i wass ideg ur ippuqeîîi yiwen, deg umkan n wayev, s wacemma; ur tepwaqbal le$ôama segs, ur t tenfaâ ccafuâa, ur ppusellken"
  2,124,"Ibôahim, mi t Ijeôôeb Mass is, s wawalen, iu$ awal. Inna: \"Nek, a k Rre$ d win ara inehhun medden\". Inna: \"u si tarwa w\"? Inna: \"lemâahda W ur taâna ara imednas"
  2,125,"Mi Nerra Axxam d lemqam i yimdanen, u d amkan n laman: \"erret lemqam n Ibôahim d loamaâ\"! Nâuhed i Ibôahim akked Ismaâil: \"zzizdget Axxam iW, i wid idewwiôen, wid ip$imin, wid iîîinizen, wid ikennun"
  2,126,"Mi inna Ibôahim: \"a Mass iw! Err wagi d tamdint n laman, £it imezda$ is s ppemôat; wid, segsen, iumnen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru\". Inna: \"win ijehlen, a t Ooe$ ad izhu cwiî, sinna, a t Nehôe$ ar uâaqeb n tmes. A tu$alin tucmip"
  2,127,"Ibôahim akked Ismaâil, mi ssalayen leêyuv n Uxxam: \"a Mass nne$! Eqbel s$uône$, Keçç, s tidep, d Win Isellen, d Amusnaw"
  2,128,"A Mass nne$! Err ane$ d imvuâen iK, u, si dderya nne$, lois ar aK ianzen. Mel a$ isekkiren nne$, Ssuref a$. Keçç, s tidep, Tessurufev, Tepêunuv"
  2,129,"A Mass nne$! Azen asen d amazan segsen, ad asen iqqaô issekniyen iK, ad asen isseêfev Tazmamt akked ûûwab, a ten izzizdeg. Keçç, s tidep, d Uzmir, d Bab n ûûwab"
  2,130,"Anwa iugin ddin n Ibôahim, siwa win iccemten iman is? Ni$ Nefren it di ddunit. Di laxeôt, neppa, war ccekk, seg iâaôviyen"
  2,131,"Mi s Inna Mass is: \"anez\"! Inna: \"unze$ aS i Mass imavalen"
  2,132,"Iweûûa yis Ibôahim arraw is - akken Iaâqub -: \"a yarraw iw, Öebbi, s tidep, Ifren awen ddin, ur ppemmtet siwa ma tunzem"
  2,133,"Ne$ tellam d inagan mi d ters tmeppant ar Yaâqub, mi inna i tarwa s: \"anwa ara tâabdem deffir i\"? Nnan: \"a naâbed Öebbi k, u Öebbi n lejdud ik: Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq. Öebbi Yiwen. Nekwni nunez aS"
  2,134,"Wigi d lois i iâaddan. Ines ayen ikseb, nnwen ayen tkesbem. Ur kwen steqsayen $ef wayen xeddmen"
  2,135,"Nnan: \"ilit d udayen ne$ d imasiêiyen, a ppepwanhum\". Ini: \"Xaîi, maca ddin n Ibôahim, imalen ar tidep. Ur illi seg imcurak"
  2,136,"Init: \"numen s Öebbi akked wayen id irsen $uône$, wayen id irsen ar Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, ayen ippunefken i Musa, Âisa, ayen ippunefken i lambiyya, s$uô Mass nnsen. Ur nessemgarrad yiwen segsen, nekwni nunez aS"
  2,137,"Ma umnen ayen icuban ayen tumnem, atnan pwanhan. Ma wexxôen, haaten kan di lefôaq. Iqadd ik Öebbi, segsen. Neppa Issel, d Amusnaw"
  2,138,"Ssbi$a, n Öebbi. Anwa yifen Öebbi i ssbi$a? Nekwni d iâabbaden iS"
  2,139,"Ini: \"day ad a$ tnamrem $ef Öebbi, u Neppa d Mass nne$, u d Mass nnwen? I nekwni igiten nne$, i kunwi igiten nnwen. Nekwni d izedganen iS"
  2,140,"Ne$ a d tinim: \"s tidep, Ibôahim, Ismaâil, Isêaq, Iaâqub, laâôac, llan d udayen, ne$ d imasiêiyen\"? Ini: \"Anwa i isnen sennig akw, d kunwi ne$ d Öebbi\"? Anwa i idensen sennig win iffren ccada, i isâa s$uô Öebbi? Ur I$fil Öebbi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  2,141,"Asatu agi iâadda. Ines ayen ikseb, nnwen ayen tkesbem. Ur fellawen asteqsi $ef wayen xeddmen"